{"word":"προσρέω","slug":"προσρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ρεύσομαι</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-ερρύην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to flow towards a point, to stream in, assemble</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to rush up to</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}